    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "= $itemIndex % 2 === 0 ? \n`You are a senior sales developer. Write a cold email for ${$json.name} in ${$json.city}.\nCONTEXT: They are a ${$json.business_category} with great reviews on Facebook, but NO professional website. \nSTRATEGY: Template 5.1 (Direct Contact).\n- Subject: Modern website concept for ${$json.name}\n- Body: Start with \"Hi\". Mention you saw their excellent reviews in ${$json.city} and their active Facebook page, but explain that a dedicated site would capture more customers from Google.\n- Link: https://sitezinho-kappa.vercel.app/?nome=${encodeURIComponent($json.name)}&cidade=${encodeURIComponent($json.city)}&tipo=${encodeURIComponent($json.business_category.split('|')[0].replace(/_/g, ' '))}&tel=${encodeURIComponent($json.phone_number)}&fb=${encodeURIComponent($json.facebook)}\n- Offer: High-conversion layout. Final version in 5 days for $500.\n- Sign: Ricardo. Under 70 words. No Markdown for links (output URL as plain text).` \n\nThis email its a correction by a wrong link sent in past email. Then ... include sorry in the content ",
        "options": {}
      },
